please refer to the routing introductory videos

23
00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:42.000
for a greater explanation of distance vector

24
00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:47.000
versus advanced distance vector versus links state routing protocols.

25
00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:51.000
